title: IX: Oedipus, Mother-Lover & Father-Killer (Oedipus Part Two)
itunes:title: IX: Oedipus, Mother-Lover & Father-Killer (Oedipus Part Two)
itunes:subtitle: Oh, Oedipus, the trouble you get into.
description:
Oh, Oedipus, the trouble you get into. Part Two involves some revelations and some more inconceivable ignorance and Oedipus' part. It's definitely not dramatic.


CW/TW: far too many Greek myths involve assault. Given it's fiction, and typically involves gods and/or monsters, I'm not as deferential as I would be were I referencing the real thing.


Attributions and licensing information for music used in the podcast can be found here: mythsbaby.com/sources-attributions.
